name: Wheel of Fortune
description:
This art piece visualizes the
primitiveness of the human emotions
going parallel with the strong
fluctuating crypto market. For many, it
is nothing but the struggle to hold on
and the hope to step up their game
over time. For the 'few' who've turned
their luck into reality, they thrive on
their established 'wealth' on the top of
the world. Beyond this 'top' you see
the fallen. They face the grim
consequences of 'the flipside to the
coin'!
